query: SELECT om.id, om.omUserId, om.omOrgId, om.omRole, u.name as userName, u.email, u.platformOwner, o.orgName, o.orgAccountId FROM org_memberships om JOIN users u ON u.id = om.omUserId JOIN organizations o ON o.id = om.omOrgId WHERE u.name LIKE '%Junaid%'
